name: Honey Stinger Organic Energy Chews Fruit Smoothie
description:
Great tasting energy snacks that include carbohydrates from multiple sources: glucose, fructose, maltose, and sucrose.Contains 95% organic ingredients. Gluten-free, dairy-free, no trans fats and no partially hydrogenated oils.Ingredients: organic tapioca syrup, organic evaporated cane juice, organic grape juice concentrate, organic honey, pectin, citric acid, ascorbic acid, color (black carrot juice concentrate (red), annatto (orange)), natural flavors, potassium citrate, organic sunflower oil, carnauba wax.
